{
  "$schema": "https://mintlify.com/docs.json",
  "theme": "luma",
  "name": "Fluid",
  "colors": {
    "primary": "#2464ec",
    "light": "#0c0c3c"
  },
  "favicon": "/favicon.svg",
  "markdown": {
    "instructions": [
      "The canonical Fluid API surface is v2026-04; endpoint paths use /api/v202604/... .",
      "Authenticate with the header Authorization: Bearer <token>; public storefront read endpoints require no auth.",
      "Lists use cursor pagination via the page[cursor] and page[limit] query params; follow meta.pagination.next_cursor until it is null.",
      "Never use /api/company/v1 or /api/v1 paths, page/per_page params, or offset pagination — they are legacy.",
      "The OpenAPI spec at api-reference/storefront-v2026-04.yaml is the authoritative contract; prefer it over prose when in doubt.",
      "Successful responses wrap the resource payload alongside a top-level integer status and a meta object."
    ]
  },
